netrisk-simulator/
├── app/
│   ├── models.py        # Institution, Exposure classes
│   ├── network.py        # Network graph + centrality
│   ├── simulation.py     # Contagion logic
│   ├── database.py        # SQLite setup
│   ├── main.py            # FastAPI app
├── data/
│   └── seed_data.py       # Generate sample institutions
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
NetworkX calculates centrality scores
        ↓
Historical simulation results stored in SQLite
        ↓
ML model trained on: centrality + dependency count + failure history
        ↓
Model predicts: "Auth Service has 78% failure risk right now"
        ↓
REST API serves prediction
